                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Management Consulting Firm</h3>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Challenge</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Manual time tracking and complex billing arrangements across multiple clients with poor visibility into project profitability and resource utilization.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Solution</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Comprehensive project management system with automated time tracking, flexible billing models, and real-time profitability analysis.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Implementation Highlights</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                  <li>• Mobile time tracking application</li>
                  <li>• Automated billing and invoicing</li>
                  <li>• Real-time project dashboards</li>
                  <li>• Resource utilization optimization</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-success-600 mb-2">50%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Faster billing process</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">35%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Project margin improvement</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">90%</div>
